# Portfolio Chat app rules

## At task start

1. Read **`apps/portfolio-chat/docs/AGENTS.md`** (read order).
2. Read **`apps/portfolio-chat/docs/context/progress-tracker.md`** (Current Goal, In Progress).

## While implementing

- Follow the active row in **`docs/feature-specs/00-index.md`** and its spec file.
- **New domains:** code under `features/<name>/` per **`docs/feature-specs/01-design-system.md`**.
- **Legacy paths** (`components/`, `lib/`, `contexts/`): touch only when the spec or task says so; prefer `features/` for new work.
- Do not invent product behavior missing from specs or `docs/prd.md`.

## Before done

- Update **`docs/context/progress-tracker.md`** (Completed, Current Goal, In Progress, Next Up, Open Questions, Session Notes as needed).
- Run **`pnpm typecheck`** from `apps/portfolio-chat` when types, routes, or API handlers changed.
- Run **`pnpm build`** when touching `app/` layout, env, or Next config.
